    <div id=\"SEDOC-1528946962465-632856126_se_doc_title_bottom\" class=\"se_doc_title_bottom\"></div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<!-- B2C 상품 -->\n<!-- _BLOG_CONTENTS_HEADER_TAIL -->\n<!-- SE_DOC_HEADER_END -->\n<div class=\"se_doc_header_end\" id=\"SEDOC-1528946962465-632856126_se_doc_header_end\"></div>\n<div class=\"se_doc_contents_start\" id=\"SEDOC-1528946962465-632856126_se_doc_contents_start\"></div>\n<!-- SE_DOC_CONTENTS_START -->\n<div class=\"se_component_wrap sect_dsc __se_component_area\">\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"se_component se_paragraph default\">\n    <div class=\"se_sectionArea\">\n        <div class=\"se_editArea\">\n            <div class=\"se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_T3 se_align-left\" >\n                <div class=\"se_editView\">\n                    <div class=\"se_textView\">\n                        <p class=\"se_textarea\"><!-- SE3-TEXT { -->이번 포스팅에서는 기질적인 병변으로 인한 비정상 출혈에 대해서 알아보도록 하겠습니다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. <br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span>주로 자궁질환으로 인한 출혈이 이 범주에 속합니다<span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><br><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><!-- } SE3-TEXT --></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\t\t<div class=\"se_component se_image default\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"se_sectionArea se_align-left\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_editArea\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_viewArea\" style=\"max-width:500px\">\n        <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"se_mediaArea __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"imgId\" : \"SEDOC-1528946962465-632856126_image_0_img\", \"src\" : \"https://familydoctor.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/shutterstock_166610351-705x461.jpg\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                            <img id=\"SEDOC-1528946962465-632856126_image_0_img\" class=\"se_mediaImage __se_img_el\" src=\"https://familydoctor.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/shutterstock_166610351-705x461.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"327\" data-attachment-id=\"\" alt=\"\">\n        \n        </a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"se_component se_paragraph default\">\n    <div class=\"se_sectionArea\">\n        <div class=\"se_editArea\">\n            <div class=\"se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_T3 se_align-left\" >\n                <div class=\"se_editView\">\n                    <div class=\"se_textView\">\n                        <p class=\"se_textarea\"><!-- SE3-TEXT { -->우선 자궁내막증식증입니다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. &nbsp;Endometrial Hyperplasia<br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span>자궁내막증식증의 출혈은 월경량이 많고<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>주기가 아닌 기간동안에 출혈이 생기는 부정기월경이 결합된 형태입니다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. <br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span>그러므로 출혈량이 많고 자주 출혈이 생기다보니 빈혈이 동반된 경우가 많습니다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. <br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span>당연히 임신에도 영향을 끼치고 조기폐경과도 연관이 있습니다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. <br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span>자궁내막증식증이 의심될 정도로 자궁내막이 두꺼워져 있는 경우에는 내막생검을 통해 조직의 변화를 검사하게 됩니다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. <br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><!-- } SE3-TEXT --></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\t\t<div class=\"se_component se_image default\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"se_sectionArea se_align-left\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_editArea\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_viewArea\" style=\"max-width:500px\">\n        <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"se_mediaArea __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"imgId\" : \"SEDOC-1528946962465-632856126_image_1_img\", \"src\" : \"https://www.askdrshah.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/Endometriosis.jpg\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                            <img id=\"SEDOC-1528946962465-632856126_image_1_img\" class=\"se_mediaImage __se_img_el\" src=\"https://www.askdrshah.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/Endometriosis.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"426\" data-attachment-id=\"\" alt=\"\">\n        \n        </a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"se_component se_paragraph default\">\n    <div class=\"se_sectionArea\">\n        <div class=\"se_editArea\">\n            <div class=\"se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_T3 se_align-left\" >\n                <div class=\"se_editView\">\n                    <div class=\"se_textView\">\n                        <p class=\"se_textarea\"><!-- SE3-TEXT { -->그 다음은 자궁내막증입니다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. Endometriosis<br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span>월경과다가 생기고<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 7</span>일이상 지속되는 생리<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>또는 생리주기짧아지는 경향을 보이기도 합니다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. <br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span>월경통이 심해지거나 성교통<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>만성골반통도 생깁니다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. <br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span>자궁내막증 역시 임신에 영향을 끼치게 됩니다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. <br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span>복강경을 통한 진단이 가장 정확하기는 하지만 복강경은 침습적인 방법이라서 증상이 심한 경우에만 시행하게 됩니다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. <br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span>증상이 심하지 않을 때는 주로 초음파를 통해 자궁내막증을 추측을 하게 됩니다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. <br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><!-- } SE3-TEXT --></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\t\t<div class=\"se_component se_image default\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"se_sectionArea se_align-left\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_editArea\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_viewArea\" style=\"max-width:500px\">\n        <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"se_mediaArea __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"imgId\" : \"SEDOC-1528946962465-632856126_image_2_img\", \"src\" : \"https://i0.wp.com/fogut.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/adenomyosis.png?fit&#61;750%2C377&amp;ssl&#61;1\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                            <img id=\"SEDOC-1528946962465-632856126_image_2_img\" class=\"se_mediaImage __se_img_el\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/fogut.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/adenomyosis.png?fit&#61;750%2C377&amp;ssl&#61;1\" width=\"500\" height=\"251\" data-attachment-id=\"\" alt=\"\">\n        \n        </a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"se_component se_paragraph default\">\n    <div class=\"se_sectionArea\">\n        <div class=\"se_editArea\">\n            <div class=\"se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_T3 se_align-left\" >\n                <div class=\"se_editView\">\n                    <div class=\"se_textView\">\n                        <p class=\"se_textarea\"><!-- SE3-TEXT { --><span><br></span><span>자궁선근증입니다. Adenomyosis.<br></span><span>자궁선근증도 과다월경과 성교시 출혈</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>월경사이 출혈이 나타날 수 있습니다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. <br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span>또한 월경통과 성교통도 나타날 수 있습니다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. <br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span>초음파를 통해 비교적 쉽게 자궁선근증을 진단할 수 있습니다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. <br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><!-- } SE3-TEXT --></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\t\t<div class=\"se_component se_image default\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"se_sectionArea se_align-justify\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_editArea\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_viewArea\" >\n        <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"se_mediaArea __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"imgId\" : \"SEDOC-1528946962465-632856126_image_3_img\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxODA2MTRfMzAw/MDAxNTI4OTQ2NDQ0OTEz.Aa8Rf_frNtJ7sZYVwuOH0glD0exYTVlSN7-7X2EyAd0g.cExQbzO8x5qE1_7lsTcec6AXNul-0r0WWHWPPW4pmdQg.JPEG.isuhani/pid-pelvic-inflammatory-disease-1-638.jpg\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                            <img id=\"SEDOC-1528946962465-632856126_image_3_img\" class=\"se_mediaImage __se_img_el\" src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxODA2MTRfMzAw/MDAxNTI4OTQ2NDQ0OTEz.Aa8Rf_frNtJ7sZYVwuOH0glD0exYTVlSN7-7X2EyAd0g.cExQbzO8x5qE1_7lsTcec6AXNul-0r0WWHWPPW4pmdQg.JPEG.isuhani/pid-pelvic-inflammatory-disease-1-638.jpg?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxODA2MTRfMzAw/MDAxNTI4OTQ2NDQ0OTEz.Aa8Rf_frNtJ7sZYVwuOH0glD0exYTVlSN7-7X2EyAd0g.cExQbzO8x5qE1_7lsTcec6AXNul-0r0WWHWPPW4pmdQg.JPEG.isuhani/pid-pelvic-inflammatory-disease-1-638.jpg?type=w580\" data-width=\"565\" data-height=\"366\" width=\"565\" height=\"366\" data-attachment-id=\"IzFL_FJVPBi4wNh9mxHPzzMJPUtM\" alt=\"\">\n        \n        </a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_editView\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_textView se_mediaCaption\">\n                                        <span class=\"se_textarea\">https://www.slideshare.net/asmaaghanem982/pid-pelvic-inflammatory-disease</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"se_component se_paragraph default\">\n    <div class=\"se_sectionArea\">\n        <div class=\"se_editArea\">\n            <div class=\"se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_T3 se_align-left\" >\n                <div class=\"se_editView\">\n                    <div class=\"se_textView\">\n                        <p class=\"se_textarea\"><!-- SE3-TEXT { --><span>골반 염증성 질환&nbsp; PID(Pelvic inflammatory disease)<br></span><span>골반 염증성 질환에서는 월경 사이 출혈</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>성교후 출혈이 생길 수 있고 분비물에서 심한 냄새가 나기도 합니다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. <br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span>골반의 문제이기 때문에 골반통이 나타나고 심하면 열이 나기도 합니다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. <br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span>다만, 만성이 된 경우에는 열이 생기는 경우가 드뭅니다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. <br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><!-- } SE3-TEXT --></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\t\t<div class=\"se_component se_image default\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"se_sectionArea se_align-left\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_editArea\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_viewArea\" style=\"max-width:500px\">\n        <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"se_mediaArea __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"imgId\" : \"SEDOC-1528946962465-632856126_image_4_img\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxODA2MTRfMTU2/MDAxNTI4OTQ2NzMxNTA5.D158sm7--M7W-K--UEycLfsUQTwkUEA2jVlscHfnEPYg.2eQgGYbwOhehXW0K9joCY6o1SCy8hApniPlBwZdpC0Ag.JPEG.isuhani/image.jpg\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                            <img id=\"SEDOC-1528946962465-632856126_image_4_img\" class=\"se_mediaImage __se_img_el\" src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxODA2MTRfMTU2/MDAxNTI4OTQ2NzMxNTA5.D158sm7--M7W-K--UEycLfsUQTwkUEA2jVlscHfnEPYg.2eQgGYbwOhehXW0K9joCY6o1SCy8hApniPlBwZdpC0Ag.JPEG.isuhani/image.jpg?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxODA2MTRfMTU2/MDAxNTI4OTQ2NzMxNTA5.D158sm7--M7W-K--UEycLfsUQTwkUEA2jVlscHfnEPYg.2eQgGYbwOhehXW0K9joCY6o1SCy8hApniPlBwZdpC0Ag.JPEG.isuhani/image.jpg?type=w580\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"488\" width=\"500\" height=\"488\" data-attachment-id=\"Iz21-Z1Z9PH3g9bxXp0Htyr4ibPc\" alt=\"\">\n        \n        </a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_editView\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_textView se_mediaCaption\">\n                                        <span class=\"se_textarea\">https://www.news-medical.net/health/What-is-an-Endometrial-Polyp-(Korean).aspx</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"se_component se_paragraph default\">\n    <div class=\"se_sectionArea\">\n        <div class=\"se_editArea\">\n            <div class=\"se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_T3 se_align-left\" >\n                <div class=\"se_editView\">\n                    <div class=\"se_textView\">\n                        <p class=\"se_textarea\"><!-- SE3-TEXT { --><span>자궁내막폴립의 경우에도 월경량이 많아지고 성교후 출혈</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>폐경후 출혈 등이 나타납니다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. <br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span>특히 폐경기 전후에 출혈이 나타나는 경우는 폴립이 원인인 경우가 많습니다<span lang=\"EN-US\">.<br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><!-- } SE3-TEXT --></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\t\t<div class=\"se_component se_image default\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"se_sectionArea se_align-justify\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_editArea\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_viewArea\" >\n        <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"se_mediaArea __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"imgId\" : \"SEDOC-1528946962465-632856126_image_5_img\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxODA2MTRfMTQ5/MDAxNTI4OTQ2ODE5NzM0._TSs5yrOoIdAkKi5XX2COsXVitkmH8uogjz0dlAL3_0g.KsrK5dIh6_eKD53IkWAjbUziKNI9DSziW3gmxVSNucog.JPEG.isuhani/Endometrial-Cancer.jpg\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                            <img id=\"SEDOC-1528946962465-632856126_image_5_img\" class=\"se_mediaImage __se_img_el\" src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxODA2MTRfMTQ5/MDAxNTI4OTQ2ODE5NzM0._TSs5yrOoIdAkKi5XX2COsXVitkmH8uogjz0dlAL3_0g.KsrK5dIh6_eKD53IkWAjbUziKNI9DSziW3gmxVSNucog.JPEG.isuhani/Endometrial-Cancer.jpg?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxODA2MTRfMTQ5/MDAxNTI4OTQ2ODE5NzM0._TSs5yrOoIdAkKi5XX2COsXVitkmH8uogjz0dlAL3_0g.KsrK5dIh6_eKD53IkWAjbUziKNI9DSziW3gmxVSNucog.JPEG.isuhani/Endometrial-Cancer.jpg?type=w580\" data-width=\"1200\" data-height=\"954\" width=\"1200\" height=\"954\" data-attachment-id=\"IBNkGswJ0u_Oox7XvXY43wJ4fYo0\" alt=\"\">\n        \n        </a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_editView\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_textView se_mediaCaption\">\n                                        <span class=\"se_textarea\">https://www.epainassist.com/pelvic-pain/uterus/endometrial-cancer-or-uterine-cancer</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"se_component se_paragraph default\">\n    <div class=\"se_sectionArea\">\n        <div class=\"se_editArea\">\n            <div class=\"se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_T3 se_align-left\" >\n                <div class=\"se_editView\">\n                    <div class=\"se_textView\">\n                        <p class=\"se_textarea\"><!-- SE3-TEXT { --><span>마지막은 암입니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">. <br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span>일단 폐경후 출혈이 생긴 경우에 내막암이 많기 때문에 주의하셔야 합니다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>보통<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 10%</span>에서 암으로 진단됩니다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>내막암의 위험인자는<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 40</span>대 이상의 고령<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>비만<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>출산하지 않은 경우<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>호르몬제를 복용하는 경우<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>당뇨병<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>가족력 등이 있으니 위험인자를 가지고 있는 경우에는 정확한 진단을 꼭 받아보시길 바랍니다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span><!-- } SE3-TEXT --></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"se_component se_paragraph default\">\n    <div class=\"se_sectionArea\">\n        <div class=\"se_editArea\">\n            <div class=\"se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_T3 se_align-left\" >\n                <div class=\"se_editView\">\n                    <div class=\"se_textView\">\n                        <p class=\"se_textarea\"><!-- SE3-TEXT { --> <span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><br><br> <span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><br> 호르몬의 불균형으로 인한 기능성 비정상 출혈이 아닌<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>기질적 원인이 의심되는 경우에는 정확한 진단 후에 치료를 받으시길 권합니다<span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><br><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><br> 출혈이 아닌<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>기질적 원인이 의심되는 경우에는 정확한 진단 후에 치료를 받으시길 권합니다<span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><!-- } SE3-TEXT --></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"se_component se_paragraph default\">\n    <div class=\"se_sectionArea\">\n        <div class=\"se_editArea\">\n            <div class=\"se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_T3 se_align-left\" >\n                <div class=\"se_editView\">\n                    <div class=\"se_textView\">\n                        <p class=\"se_textarea\"><!-- SE3-TEXT { --><!-- } SE3-TEXT --></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </